BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Surf's Up
DTSTART:20260502T073600
DTEND:20260502T110000
DESCRIPTION:TIDES:\n-0.061ft at 07:36\n-2.956ft at 11:00\n\nOBSERVATION:\n
 Lingering mix of WNW and SSW swell starts the morning off in mainly thigh 
 to waist high+ waves\, then surf slowly dips during the afternoon as the o
 ld swell eases. Draining dawn patrol negative low tide\, then the incoming
  tide push gets an assist through mid morning. Mid day high tide slows the
  smaller waves.\n\nWinds looking light/variable much of the morning\, ligh
 t SW mid day\, then shifting NW offshore for town spots over the afternoon
 . 
END:VEVENT
